          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The reason why the cost of insulin and other drugs are so disproportionately high in the U.S. is because politicians have for years crafted policy to allow pharmaceutical companies to maximally gouge American patients.",
